        {
          "en": "5 and 6"
        }
      ],
      "answerIndex": 0,
      "solution": {
        "en": "x² − 5x + 6 = (x−2)(x−3) = 0, so x = 2 or x = 3. They add to 5 and multiply to 6, matching the equation."
      }
    },
